N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4229.4 - Judges to settle disputes

State Regulations

If the dividing owners cannot agree as to which of them
is to have a cup or other prize which cannot be divided, the question shall be
determined by lot by the judges. Notes
